knowledge_graph.title: Peter J. Shields Library
knowledge_graph.type: Library in University of California-Davis, California
knowledge_graph.description: The Peter J. Shields Library, or Shields Library, is a four-story library named after Peter J. Shields. It is located in the eastern part of main campus of UC Davis in unincorporated Yolo County, adjacent to Davis.
